<span class='spoilerAnswerText'>
<a class="jsShowSpoiler spoilerAction">(view spoiler)</a><span class="spoilerContainer" style="display: none">[Was this the perfect ending or should Marco and Anne have lived happily after? They both had been through so much. I cannot decide. <a class="jsHideSpoiler spoilerAction">(hide spoiler)</a>]</span>
</span>
